\par \pard\plain \s13\sa86 \b\f2\fs16\cf2 Minesweeper Rules:
\par \pard\plain \s7\fi-360\li720\sa180\tx720 \f2\fs16 \{bmc bull.bmp\}\tab The playing area is a mine field, simulated by a grid of squares.  Initially, all the squares are covered.
\par \{bml covered.bmp\}A covered square
\par \{bmc bull.bmp\}\tab To uncover a square, you step on it.  You continue to uncover squares until only the squares containing mines are covered.
\par \{bmc bull.bmp\}\tab If you step on a square that contains a mine, the game is over and all the mines are displayed.
\par \{bml mine.bmp\}A mine square
\par \{bmc bull.bmp\}\tab If you step on a square that does not contain a mine, it is replaced by either a number or a blank.  If the square is replaced by a number, {\i N}, then there are {\i N}
 mines in the surrounding eight squares.  If the square is replaced by a blank, there are no mines in the surrounding eight squares.
\par \{bml blank.bmp\}A blank square
\par \{bml num.bmp\}A number square
\par \{bml number.bmp\}Here, there are three mines in the surrounding eight squares.
\par \{bmc bull.bmp\}\tab If you step on a square, and it is replaced by a blank, the surrounding eight squares are uncovered automatically because there cannot be any mines under them.
\par \{bmc bull.bmp\}\tab If you know a square is a mine, you can {\ul mark}{\v Mark} the square.  You cannot step on a marked square.
\par \{bml marked.bmp\}A marked square
\par \{bmc bull.bmp\}\tab You can also clear around an uncovered number square.  Clearing around an uncovered number square uncovers any of the surrounding eight squares which are unmarked. 
\par \pard \s7\li720\sa180\tx1080 {\cf6 Note:}  You are not allowed to clear around a square if you have not marke
d enough mines in the surrounding eight squares, or if the square is covered.  For example, if you try to clear around a square labeled 3, and you have marked only two squares with mines, nothing will happen.  Or, if you try to clear around an uncovered s
quare, nothing will happen.  
\par \pard \s7\fi-360\li720\sa180\tx720 \{bml befbs.bmp\}If you clear around the center square . . . 
\par \{bml aftbs.bmp\} . . . the surrounding unmarked squares are uncovered.
\par \{bmc bull.bmp\}\tab If you clear around an uncovered number square, and there is an unmarked mine in the surrounding eight squares, it is uncovered and the game is over.
\par \{bml befbsm.bmp\}Here, if you clear around the center square . . .
\par \{bml aftbsm.bmp\} . . . a mine is uncovered and the game is over.
\par \{bmc bull.bmp\}\tab Play continues until you either uncover all squares without mines or until you uncover a mine and die.
